Summary: Sudden bright streak overhead out-of nowhere seemed like really close star
divs: Sighting DetailsSitting down in bus stop staring at tree line and all of a sudden a bright streak from what looked like a star darted roughly 60 degrees above horizon all the way behind me in a second or less so. Too fast.
